| Connection Direction | Controller â†’ Agent | Agent â†’ Controller | N/A â€“ Local Container | Controller â†’ Cloud API |
| Requires Java        | âœ…                  | âœ…                  | âŒ (in image)          | Depends                |
| Dynamic Provisioning | âŒ                  | âŒ                  | âœ…                     | âœ…                      |
